# The Setup Menus

## EDIT/SAVE QUICK MENU (Still Photography)
Choose the items displayed in the quick menu during still photography (page 311).

## EDIT/SAVE QUICK MENU (Movies)
Choose the items displayed in the quick menu when filming movies (page 311).

## FUNCTION (Fn) SETTING
Choose the roles played by the function buttons (page 317).

## POWER ZOOM LENS FUNCTION (Fn) SETTING
Choose the roles played by the function buttons available on some power zoom lenses (page 325).
